    "currency": "EUR",
    "notes": "French civil service pay = indice majoré (IM) × valeur du point d'indice (€4.92278/month, frozen since July 2023 per Décret 2023-519). Annual = IM × 4.92278 × 12 = monthly × 12. Three corps administratifs généraux covered: Adjoint administratif (cat C, 3 grades), Secrétaire administratif (cat B, 3 grades), Attaché d'administration CIGEM (cat A, 3 active grades + Échelon spécial HEA). These are the standard cross-ministry corps used by ~30% of fonctionnaires; specialized corps (police, magistrats, enseignants, ingénieurs) have their own grilles and are not included here. Hors-échelle letter grades (HEA1/A2/A3) for Attaché hors classe échelon spécial appear with fixed values not on the IM scale."
  },
